                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-75-off444 t18150215-75-cd445"></join> of two blankets value 5 s. a pair of sheets, value 4 s. and a counterpane value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18150215-75-victim632" type="victimName">
